                  <span class="c00">Very true. Another great insight is: &quot;<i>The end results proved that customers could tell the difference.</i>&quot;<p>Customers can always tell the difference between quality and non-quality, and since manufacturing is actually a small part of the retail price, it&#x27;s crazy to try to save money on quality.<span>
